social_posts.post_text: Merry Christmas & Happy Holidays! Can’t wait to see y’all in the new year! 🙏🏾💪🏾❤️😎

It's about that time y'all! 😎

Written by the incredible @kenblakeporter , illustrated by me, and lettered by Lucas Gattoni, Superboy: The Man of Tomorrow #1 is in stores April 18th! The FOC date is this Sunday March 26th!!! So please pre-order now! @dcofficial 

and check out these awesome variant covers! 😍🔥 Thank you @kwinones @marsisanartist @davidtalaskidraws @georgekambadais 
For your super contributions!!! 

Also!!! special thanks to our amazing editor Andrew! 🙏🏾

SUPERBOY: THE MAN OF TOMORROW #1 is out now!!! 

Hope y’all enjoy it! 🫣🙏🏾💪🏾❤️
#Superboy: Man of tomorrow #3 is out now!!!!! 🙏🏾💪🏾❤️🔥
#Superboy Man Of Tomorrow #4 is in stores now!!! With variants from @toddnauck and @meganhuang5! I hope y’all can feel how much fun I’m having! 🫣😁
See you at FanExpo! Table P52!! 🙏🏾💪🏾❤️
FANEXPO starts today!!! Come say hi 👋🏾 table P52
